<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TMaL15">
<l>meyyarkkē meyya ṉākum vitiyilā veṉṉaip pōla</l>
<l>poyyarkkē poyya ṉākum puṭkoṭi yuṭaiya kōmā</l>
<l>ṉuyyappō muṇarvi ṉārkaṭ koruvaṉeṉ ṟuṇarnta piṉṉai</l>
<l>aiyappā ṭaṟuttut tōṉṟu maḻakaṉū raraṅka maṉṟē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The King with the bird banner is truthful to the true people</l>
<l rend="indent">[and] false to the false ones</l>
<l rend="indent">like me without good fortune.</l>
<l>Raṅgam is the town of the Handsome [Lord]</l>
<l>who appears after removing the doubts</l>
<l>of those conscious about being redeemed</l>
<l>after they understand that He is the One, is it not?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
